OL,3,CFormer Sinn Fein press officer jailed
OL,4,Cfor child sex offences
OL,6,FA former Sinn Fein press officer has
OL,7,Fbeen jailed for nine months after
OL,8,Fpleading guilty to a series of child
OL,9,Fsex offences.
OL,11,FMichael McMonagle, 43, from Limewood
OL,12,FStreet in Londonderry, was sentenced
OL,13,Fat Derry Crown Court to nine months in
OL,14,Fcustody and nine months under
OL,15,Fstatutory supervision.
