OL,3,CFormer Sinn Fein press officer jailed
OL,4,Cfor child sex offences
OL,6,FHe made no comment as he arrived at
OL,7,Fcourt earlier in the case that plunged
OL,8,FSinn Fein into controversy as it faced
OL,9,Fquestions around safeguarding, and how
OL,10,Ftwo other party press officers
OL,11,Fprovided references for McMonagle for
OL,12,Fa subsequent job with the British
OL,13,FHeart Foundation.
OL,15,FDerry Crown Court heard on Friday how
OL,16,FMcMonagle had communicated with a
OL,17,Fnumber of online accounts which were
OL,18,Frun by police officers posing as six
OL,19,Fchildren aged between 12 and under 16
OL,20,Fyears.
